{"word":"Tarshish","slug":"tarshish","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Tarshish</b> <a href=\"#/H8659\">H8659</a> <br/> 1. Son of Javan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=4'>Gen 10:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=7'>1Ch 1:7</a><br/> 2. A city, called also Tharshish:<br/> - Possibly Spain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=5'>Gen 10:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=72&verse=10'>Psa 72:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=66&verse=19'>Isa 66:19</a> <br/> - Solomon makes valuable imports from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=22'>1Ki 10:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=21'>2Ch 9:21</a> <br/> - Commerce and wealth of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=22'>1Ki 10:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=48'>1Ki 22:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=21'>2Ch 9:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=36'>2Ch 20:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=48&verse=7'>Psa 48:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=16'>Isa 2:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=23&verse=14'>Isa 23:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=9'>Isa 60:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=9'>Jer 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=12'>Eze 27:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=25'>Eze 27:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=38&verse=13'>Eze 38:13</a> <br/> - Jonah would flee to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibl